WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.466 --> 00:00:02.200
Don’t harm the Empress Dowager any further.

2
00:00:02.200 --> 00:00:05.833
I’ve cursed them all, cursed them all!

3
00:00:07.566 --> 00:00:08.966
They told us we can’t

4
00:00:08.966 --> 00:00:10.600
give them the antidote.

5
00:00:11.100 --> 00:00:13.566
I want them to live in pain for all eternity.

6
00:00:13.566 --> 00:00:18.433
It’s all my fault, Empress Dowager. Ah, ah!

7
00:00:20.700 --> 00:00:22.400
Don’t think you’ll be any better off.

8
00:00:23.066 --> 00:00:25.900
The Empress Dowager has already drunk the tea I gave her today.

9
00:00:25.900 --> 00:00:27.500
Without the antidote,

10
00:00:27.766 --> 00:00:29.800
she will die within ten days.

11
00:00:30.866 --> 00:00:32.366
You have such a ruthless heart.

12
00:00:32.466 --> 00:00:34.033
You seem gentle and kind,

13
00:00:34.366 --> 00:00:36.700
but inside you are more sinister than anyone.

14
00:00:36.966 --> 00:00:38.800
You forced me into this.

15
00:00:39.300 --> 00:00:42.433
Hmph, if you had obediently followed my orders,

16
00:00:42.566 --> 00:00:44.400
I wouldn’t have resorted to this.

17
00:00:44.900 --> 00:00:46.800
It’s too late to say anything now.

18
00:00:46.800 --> 00:00:50.200
Hahaha, you’re rejoicing too soon.

19
00:00:50.866 --> 00:00:54.100
The Empress Dowager never drank that cup of tea.

20
00:00:54.333 --> 00:00:55.400
Impossible.

21
00:00:56.166 --> 00:00:58.466
I saw her drink it with my own eyes.

22
00:01:10.600 --> 00:01:12.666
Don’t believe it, Empress Dowager.

23
00:01:12.766 --> 00:01:14.266
The matter is as it is.

24
00:01:14.266 --> 00:01:16.600
I cannot afford to make any more mistakes.

25
00:01:17.700 --> 00:01:19.900
Your Majesty, please see.

26
00:01:19.900 --> 00:01:22.966
If the Empress Dowager dies, it is all my doing.

27
00:01:23.066 --> 00:01:26.100
I will immediately present the antidote to the Empress Dowager.

28
00:01:26.500 --> 00:01:27.933
Your Majesty, please see.

29
00:01:27.933 --> 00:01:30.266
Your Majesty, please!

30
00:01:34.166 --> 00:01:36.233
What have you done to the Empress Dowager?

31
00:01:36.300 --> 00:01:37.766
Who exactly are you?
